:paragraph {\"className\":\"mk-paragraph mk-paragraph-44A mkb-ia6dUuRPr\",\"blockID\":\"mkb-ia6dUuRPr\",\"globalSlug\":\"mk-paragraph-44A\",\"interactPreview\":false} -->\n<p class=\"mk-paragraph mk-paragraph-44A mkb-ia6dUuRPr\">DecentralGPT is a distributed inference computing network for AGI generation, accelerating AI development through blockchain technology. It primarily serves groups with needs in code generation, healthcare, content writing, explaining complex topics, data analysis, knowledge acquisition, sales analysis, and more. The comparable web product is ChatGPT, with a potential user base exceeding 3 billion people.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- /wp:mk-block/collapse-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:mk-block/collapse-item {\"blockID\":\"mkb-LgE0K21yI\",\"headingTagName\":\"h3\",\"heading\":\"What are the advantages of DecentralGPT over ChatGPT?\",\"iconExpand\":{\"library\":\"MooKwaiIcon\",\"slug\":\"top\",\"size\":\"medium\"},\"iconFold\":{\"library\":\"MooKwaiIcon\",\"slug\":\"bottom\",\"size\":\"medium\"},\"initExpand\":\"expandFirst\"} -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"mk-paragraph mk-paragraph-44A mkb-ewOSk7RBe\",\"blockID\":\"mkb-ewOSk7RBe\",\"globalSlug\":\"mk-paragraph-44A\"} -->\n<p class=\"mk-paragraph mk-paragraph-44A mkb-ewOSk7RBe\">a) Cost advantage in GPU computing power: Idle GPUs globally can join the DecentralGPT Network to provide computation, thereby utilizing idle GPU resources and significantly reducing costs.<br>b) DecentralGPT does not develop models itself, creating a free-competitive environment for model developers. They only need to focus on technology without worrying about the source of GPU computing resources or users, which accelerates technological iteration.<br>c) DecentralGPT provides API interfaces that are decentralized. Since they are not centralized, the interfaces cannot be blocked against a specific entity. Anyone and any organization can freely call the API interfaces, allowing different applications to develop the