rit','closed','closed','','logo','','','2024-05-25 11:37:30','2024-05-25 03:37:30','',0,'https://de-gpt.lxx.design/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/logo.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(626,1,'2024-05-24 21:27:24','2024-05-24 13:27:24','<!-- wp:mk-block/section {\"blockID\":\"mkb-7MmF3OeW8\",\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"main\"}} -->\n<section class=\"mk-section mkb-7MmF3OeW8\"><!-- wp:mk-block/box {\"blockID\":\"mkb-Ui2LdI-_Z\"} -->\n<div class=\"mk-box mkb-Ui2LdI-_Z\"><!-- wp:heading {\"className\":\"mk-heading mkb-WerOLvm91\",\"blockID\":\"mkb-WerOLvm91\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"mk-heading mkb-WerOLvm91\">Mining Rewards</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:mk-block/box {\"blockID\":\"mkb-ZGPkql_Nu\"} -->\n<div class=\"mk-box mkb-ZGPkql_Nu\"><!-- wp:mk-block/box {\"blockID\":\"mkb-SztxSjdUj\"} -->\n<div class=\"mk-box mkb-SztxSjdUj\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"mk-paragraph mk-paragraph-QD_ mkb-5KzfBqBZm\",\"blockID\":\"mkb-5KzfBqBZm\",\"globalSlug\":\"mk-paragraph-QD_\"} -->\n<p class=\"mk-paragraph mk-paragraph-QD_ mkb-5KzfBqBZm\">A total of 100 trillion tokens, 40% are allocated as mining rewards, with a halving event every 4 years.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:mk-block/box -->\n\n<!-- wp:mk-block/box {\"blockID\":\"mkb-u3x4aUwHv\"} -->\n<div class=\"mk-box mkb-u3x4aUwHv\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"mk-paragraph mk-paragraph-QD_ mkb-nw4FOUMhX\",\"blockID\":\"mkb-nw4FOUMhX\",\"globalSlug\":\"mk-paragraph-QD_\"} -->\n<p class=\"mk-paragraph mk-paragraph-QD_ mkb-nw4FOUMhX\">Machines connected to the network can earn DGC rewards for each successful user request they process. GPU machines must be leased long-term within the DBC network by staking DBC; otherwise, they will not receive DGC rewards.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:mk-block/box --></div>\n<!-- /wp:mk-block/box -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"className\":\"mk-heading mkb-K0pj3wVCE\",\"blockID\":\"mkb-K0pj3wVCE\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"mk-heading mkb-K0pj3wVCE\">Rewards are distributed e