or:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#ffffff\" class=\"has-inline-color\">Discord</mark></strong> tasks.<br>&nbsp;<br>The total amount of DecentralGPT is 100 billion, of which <strong><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#ffffff\" class=\"has-inline-color\">40%</mark></strong> is produced by <strong><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#ffffff\" class=\"has-inline-color\">mining</mark></strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:mk-block/box --></div>\n<!-- /wp:mk-block/box --></div>\n<!-- /wp:mk-block/section -->\n\n<!-- wp:mk-block/section {\"blockID\":\"mkb-lTdNvqina\",\"tagName\":\"div\",\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"video\"}} -->\n<div class=\"mk-section mkb-lTdNvqina\"><!-- wp:mk-block/button {\"blockID\":\"mkb-bgxTLZB3w\",\"globalSlug\":\"mk-button-nLo\",\"anchor\":\"videobutton\",\"provideHasLink\":true} -->\n<a class=\"mk-button mk-button-nLo mkb-bgxTLZB3w\" id=\"videobutton\"><!-- wp:mk-block/svg {\"blockID\":\"mkb-PtFiyulok\",\"mediaID\":107,\"xml\":\"\\u003csvg width=\\u002218\\u0022 height=\\u002219\\u0022 viewBox=\\u00220 0 18 19\\u0022 xmlns=\\u0022http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\u0022\\u003e\\n\\u003cpath d=\\u0022M16.5126 7.71886C17.9663 8.46134 17.9663 10.5387 16.5126 11.2811L3.40969 17.9732C2.07896 18.6529 0.500001 17.6863 0.500001 16.1921L0.500002 2.80792C0.500002 1.31368 2.07896 0.347133 3.40969 1.02678L16.5126 7.71886Z\\u0022/\\u003e\\n\\u003c/svg\\u003e\\n\\n\",\"linkEnable\":false} -->\n<span class=\"mk-svg mkb-PtFiyulok\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"19\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 19\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M16.5126 7.71886C17.9663 8.46134 17.9663 10.5387 16.5126 11.2811L3.40969 17.9732C2.07896 18.6529 0.500001 17.6863 0.500001 16.1921L0.500002 2.80792C0.500002 1.31368 2.07896 0.347133 3.40969 1.02678L16.5126 7.71886Z\"/>\n</svg>\n\n</span>\n<!-- /wp:mk-block/svg --></a>\n<!-- /wp:mk-block/button -->\n\n<!-- wp:mk-block/box {\"blockID\":\"mkb-gRY3gemkM\",\"bgMedia\":{\"enable\":true,\"mediaType\":\"vid