 rewards, with a plan to reward 400 billion tokens over 100 years, halving every 4 years. Rewards are distributed every 120 blocks(approximately 1 hour), with each distribution totaling 5,707,763 DGC.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:mk-block/box --></div>\n<!-- /wp:mk-block/box -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"className\":\"mk-heading mk-heading-9c3 mkb-rBE7yKLJK\",\"blockID\":\"mkb-rBE7yKLJK\",\"globalSlug\":\"mk-heading-9c3\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"mk-heading mk-heading-9c3 mkb-rBE7yKLJK\">The mining reward<br>allocation mechanism</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"mk-paragraph mkb-baIBkp553\",\"blockID\":\"mkb-baIBkp553\"} -->\n<p class=\"mk-paragraph mkb-baIBkp553\">70% to miners, 30% to large-scale model developers.<br>Destroy mechanism: Users can pay DGC tokens to obtain usage rights on a daily, weekly, monthly, or quarterly basis, with the paid DGC tokens being instantly destroyed 100%. Each user can send a maximum of 200 requests every 24 hours.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:mk-block/box --></section>\n<!-- /wp:mk-block/section -->','Tokenomics','','inherit','closed','closed','','37-revision-v1','','','2024-05-26 23:21:57','2024-05-26 15:21:57','',37,'https://de-gpt.lxx.design/?p=783',0,'revision','',0),(784,1,'2024-05-26 23:22:39','2024-05-26 15:22:39','<!-- wp:template-part {\"slug\":\"header\",\"theme\":\"mookwai\",\"tagName\":\"template\",\"lock\":{\"move\":true,\"remove\":true},\"className\":\"mk-part-Bh-hK8\",\"blockID\":\"mkb-x6DmWBYtj\"} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:mk-block/section {\"blockID\":\"mkb-LvuAiJ7Tn\",\"tagName\":\"div\",\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"top文字\"}} -->\n<div class=\"mk-section mkb-LvuAiJ7Tn\"><!-- wp:mk-block/box {\"blockID\":\"mkb-Ecy4ExyBn\"} -->\n<div class=\"mk-box mkb-Ecy4ExyBn\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1,\"className\":\"mk-heading mk-heading-9c3 mkb-Kf1V16JQQ\",\"blockID\":\"mkb-Kf1V16JQQ\",\"globalSlug\":\"mk-heading-9c3\"} -->\n<h1 class=\"mk-heading mk-heading-9c3 