-5KzfBqBZm\",\"globalSlug\":\"mk-paragraph-QD_\"} -->\n<p class=\"mk-paragraph mk-paragraph-QD_ mkb-5KzfBqBZm\">A total of 1000B tokens, 40% are allocated as mining rewards, with a halving event every 4 years.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:mk-block/box -->\n\n<!-- wp:mk-block/box {\"blockID\":\"mkb-u3x4aUwHv\"} -->\n<div class=\"mk-box mkb-u3x4aUwHv\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"mk-paragraph mk-paragraph-QD_ mkb-nw4FOUMhX\",\"blockID\":\"mkb-nw4FOUMhX\",\"globalSlug\":\"mk-paragraph-QD_\"} -->\n<p class=\"mk-paragraph mk-paragraph-QD_ mkb-nw4FOUMhX\">Machines connected to the network can earn DGC rewards for each successful user request they process. GPU machines must be leased long-term within the DBC network by staking DBC; otherwise, they will not receive DGC rewards.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:mk-block/box --></div>\n<!-- /wp:mk-block/box -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"className\":\"mk-heading mkb-K0pj3wVCE\",\"blockID\":\"mkb-K0pj3wVCE\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"mk-heading mkb-K0pj3wVCE\">Rewards are distributed every 120 blocks (approximately every hour), with a total reward of 5,707,763 DGC per distribution. Miners can claim their rewards at any time, and once one miner claims the reward for a block, all other miners will automatically receive their share.</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"mk-paragraph mk-paragraph-QD_ mkb-JzivjGEkw\",\"blockID\":\"mkb-JzivjGEkw\",\"globalSlug\":\"mk-paragraph-QD_\"} -->\n<p class=\"mk-paragraph mk-paragraph-QD_ mkb-JzivjGEkw\">The amount of DGC awarded to machines is calculated based on the proportion of computational power within the DBC network. For example, if Machine A has a computational power value of 1000 and the total computational power is 1,000,000, then Machine A would receive 1% of the DGC token rewards.<br><br>The price users pay for a monthly subscription is 100% automatically and immediately destroyed in real-time.<br><br>Model developers can receive 30% of the mining rewards, while GPU mining machines can receive 70% of the mining rewards.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:mk-block/box {\"blockID\":\"mkb-bI5Y2tpE-\",\"bgMedia\":{\"enable\":true,\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"image\":\"467@\\u0026https://www.decentralgpt.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/nodesbg.jpg\"}} -->\n<div class=\"mk-box relative mkb-bI5Y2tpE-\"><div class=\"mk-background-media\"><picture><img src=\"https://www.decentralgpt.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/nodesbg.jpg\" alt=\"Background media\"/></picture></div><!-- wp:mk-block/box {\"blockID\":\"mkb-eZg_hh1U3\"} -->\n<div class=\"mk-box mkb-eZg_hh1U3\"><!-- wp:heading {\"className\":\"mk-heading mk-heading-9c3 mkb-Dibk4Hpr2\",\"blockID\":\"mkb-Dibk4Hpr2\",\"globalSlug\":\"mk-heading-9c3\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"mk-heading mk-heading-9c3 mkb-Dibk4Hpr2\">GPU Mining Machine</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:mk-block/button {\"blockID\":\"mkb-iFRqXi2BV\",\"globalSlug\":\"mk-button-Mva\",\"cssClass\":[\"top-button\"],\"provideHasLink\":true,\"link\":{\"type\":\"url\",\"theLink\":\"/comming-soon/\"},\"ariaLabel\":\"comming soon\"} -->\n<a class=\"mk-button mk-button-Mva mkb-iFRqXi2BV top-button\" href=\"/comming-soon/\" aria-label=\"comming soon\"><!-- wp:mk-block/svg {\"blockID\":\"mkb-ERUGnTPoi\",\"mediaID\":67,\"xml\":\"\\u003csvg width=\\u002226\\u0022 height=\\u002226\\u0022 viewBox=\\u00220 0 26 26\\u0022 fill=\\u0022none\\u0022 xmlns=\\u0022http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\u0022\\u003e\\n\\u003cpath d=\\u0022M4.33334 21.6667C4.33334 19.5 4.33334 5.41667 4.33334 5.41667C4.33334 3.62174 5.88543 2.16667 7.8 2.16667H21.6667V19.5C21.6667 19.5 10.8233 19.5 7.8 19.5C5.07122 19.5 4.33334 19.8706 4.33334 21.6667Z\\u0022 stroke=\\u0022#080808\\u0022 stroke-width=\\u00222\\u0022 stroke-linejoin=\\u0022round\\u0022/\\u003e\\n\\u003cpath fill-rule=\\u0022evenodd\\u0022 clip-rule=\\u0022evenodd\\u0022 d=\\u0022M6.5 23.8333H21.6667V19.5H6.5C5.30338 19.5 4.33334 20.4701 4.33334 21.6667C4.33334 22.8633 5.30338 23.833